receiving the burning jewelry from medea creusa - also known by the name glauce , e.g. in apollodorus 's bibliotheca 1.9.28 . - was the daughter of king creon of corinth , greece , in whose favor jason abandoned medea .

more mythological mistakes : jason 's new wife creusa should n't have tried on the gown this sorceress sent her : it was poisoned

